The amount that is debited from the Funding Account (sending consumer's account) will be the amount 'pushed' to the recipient via a payment transfer request.  Funds can be transferred from Mastercard® or Maestro® debit card accounts. To initiate the funding transaction, users can provide the sending consumer's Primary Account Number (PAN) or a unique identifier previously mapped to the sending consumer's account.
